  "body": "```\ncontract constantState {\n    uint constant public test = block.number;\n}\n```\n\nEvery time I call test() I get the current block number. I thought the block number would be written into state during contract creation.\n\n```\n> constantstate.test()\n31892\n> constantstate.test()\n31892\n> constantstate.test()\n31893\n> constantstate.test()\n31902\n```\n",
